title: Kubernetes: Persistent Volumes
agents: kubernetes
catalog: containerization/kubernetes
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check and the associated special agent (agent_kubernetes) are deprecated
 and will be removed in Checkmk version 2.2.0.

 Please configure the new special agent using the "Kubernetes" ruleset.

 This check monitors a persistent volume in a kubernetes cluster.
 The check returns {OK} if a volume is bound otherwise {CRIT}.

discovery:
 One service is created for each persistent volume.

item:
 The name of the persistent volume.
